<td align="left" valign="top"><p>This is Sheldon Simms own font, and it's absolutely great, too.<br>
    If you like ProFont, you'll like this, too. And if you <strong>don't</strong> like ProFont,
    you'll maybe be satisfied with this one.<br>
    Sheldon made the windows version that I converted to Macintosh bitmap font file format. The
    Windows file has some versions that are not in contained in the Mac file.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>And if you still wonder what I'm talking about, you're probably no programmer or you don't like
    small fonts at all ...<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p>
